  "title": "Finance Assistant / Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Invoice Issuance and ensure all supporting documents are complete and properly maintained.</li><li>Banking of cash/cheque received promptly, record receipts in the ERP system to ensure accurate financial tracking.</li><li>Trade Finance Documentation</li><li>Monitor outstanding trade debts and follow up on collections.</li><li>Prepare periodic reports on debt aging and highlight overdue accounts.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Accountancy, or equivalent.</li><li>Detail-oriented with good time management and follow-up skills.</li><li>Good interpersonal skills with the ability to interact with all levels of staff</li></ul>",
